title: Just a couple of questions
body:
Just some Questions
1.  Talon's pickrate was 20% about 2 weeks ago and now it dropped back to 4%, why is he still not popular?
2. Why is Lux's pickrate 54% all of a sudden, why? 
3.  Why is Lee Sin not nerfed yet?
4.  Why the hell is Urgot on the free rotation
5.  Why do people call Talon broken?
